oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Gravesite of Frank E. Adkins
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Gravesite of Frank E. Adkins, Greenwood Cemetery, Clarksville, Tennessee. Frank was killed in a plane crash in Freeport, Texas on February 23, 1945.
